---
title: Sausage and Peppers on a Bun with Garlic Broccoli
description: One tray... with one mission... sausage and peppers on a bun. A quick broil of the peppers and sausage lets all the juices and spices blend together. The flavour keeps on coming with a sprinkle of cheese and drizzle of marinara sauce on the buns and a tasty side of pan-roasted broccoli tossed in garlic butter.
